name: StrikeX
public_notice: StrikeCoin (STRIKE) has recently rebranded to StrikeX (STRX). For more information, please visit their website.

description.en: StrikeX is the native currency of the blockchain powered eco-system developed & deployed by the UK Registered Company StrikeX Technologies Ltd. Their flag ship product, TradeStrike, will utilise the power of tokenisation to offer trading in Stocks, Cryptocurrencies, NFT’s & even Real Estate. Fully compliant, fully collateralised trading, 24/7 – 365 days a year. #ForThePeople.
